{"tid":2161242,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"邱騰華:將與美討論港產品標示中國製造問題","createTime":"2020-08-17T12:32:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T12:48:03.000Z","uid":75656,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"aae9a2d04ceb3a409037648940e779610e20c09b","tid":2161242,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:32:01.000Z","msg":"商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華對CNBC表示，中國和美國關係趨於緊張對香港無益，他將與美國討論香港出口至美國產品標示為中國製造的議題。<br />\n<br />\n美國政府上周發布的通知，從香港出口至美國的產品自9月25日起須標示為中國製造。邱騰華強調，世貿組織(WTO)規定，闡明香港有權可以自行標明出口品的產地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/hongkong/article/2554312\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F2554312&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21AUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=cbaa1351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/hongkong/article/2554312</a><br />\n<br />\nCNBC:<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2020/08/17/us-china-tensions-unhelpful-for-hong-kong-amid-coronavirus-pandemic.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2020%2F08%2F17%2Fus-china-tensions-unhelpful-for-hong-kong-amid-coronavirus-pandemic.html&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21AUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=48d14f0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2020/08/17/us-china-tensions-unhelpful-for-hong-kong-amid-coronavirus-pandemic.html</a>"},{"pid":"dba3d745ead5431d0b9f1990429f5106f1f143b8","tid":2161242,"uid":255637,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:33:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊撚個會同你討論 依家係我出命令要你改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你老幾呀 垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd75cc37b53800f8df2a690a118079908ff5b1d","tid":2161242,"uid":2054,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T12:33:45.000Z","msg":"多謝邱騰華支持港獨"},{"pid":"7b5a90c97111c011c4aab1c529c1ea